    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Well, I figured out that our `createURL` function was deleting items of `routeState` after supposedly copying the object into another one, storing in history an incomplete `routeState`.\r\n\r\nSorry for the inconvenience and I hope that it will be useful to someone else in the future: don't touch `routeState` in places you shouldn't be.",
